QuestData.Title: Strange Organ
QuestData.Description:
<You find a strange organ in the corpse of the mindbender. Upon picking it up, your head begins to throb.
The octopus-like creatures have long been one of Azeroth's mysteries, this organ may shed some light on them.
Someone in Newhome may know more.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Strange Organ to Finder Palta in Newhome in Nazjatar.
